Subject: [v4 3/7] drm/mediatek: add dsi reg commit disable control
Date:   Sat, 1 Jun 2019 17:26:11 +0800
Message-ID: <20190601092615.67917-4-jitao.shi@mediatek.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.21.0
